<h1 id="04-easyscreencast">04. <a href="https://extensions.gnome.org/extension/690/easyscreencast/">EasyScreenCast</a></h1>
<p>This is a fantastic extension for recording your Gnome desktop. You can record any selected area with Easy Screencast. This extension has video and audio recording at the same time.</p>

<p><img src="/assets/img/gnome/04-easyscreencast.jpg" alt="Drop Down Terminal" /></p>

<p><a class="btn btn-lg btn-danger" href="https://extensions.gnome.org/extension/690/easyscreencast/"> Get EasyScreenCast </a></p>

<hr />

<h1 id="05-open-weather">05. <a href="https://extensions.gnome.org/extension/750/openweather/">Open Weather</a></h1>
<p>Open Weather is a productivity extension that shows your current weather conditions, such as temperature, wind speed, humidity, etc. You will get all the information at openweathermap.org or forecast.io. You can customize it in different ways in Gnome Shell.</p>

<p><img src="/assets/img/gnome/05-open_weather.jpg" alt="Open Weather" /></p>

<p><a class="btn btn-lg btn-danger" href="https://extensions.gnome.org/extension/750/openweather/"> Get Open Weather </a></p>

