<h1 id="08-applications-menu">08. <a href="https://extensions.gnome.org/extension/6/applications-menu/">Applications Menu</a></h1>
<p>The Applications Menu is a fantastic extension that will help you organize all your applications according to different categories. It is part of the classic Ubuntu Gnome mode and is now officially supported for everyone.</p>

<p><img src="/assets/img/gnome/08-applications_menu.jpg" alt="Applications Menu" /></p>

<p><a class="btn btn-lg btn-danger" href="https://extensions.gnome.org/extension/6/applications-menu/"> Get the Applications Menu </a></p>

