<h1 id="09-todotxt">09. <a href="https://extensions.gnome.org/extension/570/todotxt/">Todo.txt</a></h1>
<p>Very useful for managing all activities of your Linux operating system, such as creating or deleting new tasks. When you are done with any task, mark them as complete with this extension.</p>

<p><img src="/assets/img/gnome/09-todo_txt.jpg" alt="Todo.txt" /></p>

<p><a class="btn btn-lg btn-danger" href="https://extensions.gnome.org/extension/570/todotxt/"> Get the whole.txt </a></p>

