<h1 id="11-appfolders-management-extension">11. <a href="https://extensions.gnome.org/extension/1217/appfolders-manager/">Appfolders Management extension</a></h1>
<p>An easy way to organize your applications into folders, directly from the application grid. Create folders and add / remove applications using drag and drop, rename / delete them with a right click.</p>

<p><img src="/assets/img/gnome/11-app-folders.jpg" alt="Appfolders Management extension" /></p>

