<h1 id="14-gsconnect">14. <a href="https://extensions.gnome.org/extension/1319/gsconnect/">GSConnect</a></h1>
<p>GSConnect is a complete KDE Connect implementation, especially for the GNOME Shell with integration with Nautilus, Chrome and Firefox. It does not depend on the KDE Connect desktop application and will not work only with it installed.</p>

<p><img src="/assets/img/gnome/14-gsconnect.jpg" alt="GSConnect" /></p>

<p><a class="btn btn-lg btn-danger" href="https://extensions.gnome.org/extension/1319/gsconnect/"> Get GSConnect </a></p>

